A Redis Client Library For C++

Author:
zhangyafeikimi

Features:
1. all mode supported(pipeline, trasaction, subscribe, monitor)
2. client connection pool
3. fixed-size partition client

Build and Installation:
1. librediscxx depends on boost(>=1.35) and libboost_thread is required to be linked into the final binaries.
2. Building in linux(only supported) requires SCons.
3. Windows build is no longer maintained.
